{"tid":1661476,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中大校長閉門會議","createTime":"2019-10-18T06:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T09:28:29.000Z","uid":206594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb514fa28ed0dab91364d4679475ad74dc4d590","tid":1661476,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"發覺都幾多人無follow點解而家啲中大學生會轉軚撐校長<br />\n下面就有報導詳細講返個會傾過啲咩<br />\n<br />\n//2019年10月10日，香港中文大學的校方於早上九時多發電郵給學生及教職員，指當晚五時半開始將會舉行校長公開討論會。傍晚，千人討論會甫開始，學生便謾罵聲四起，需要主持人多次暫停對話，以作調停。一眾不滿的學生在討論會完結時圍堵段崇智校長，要求與其進行「真正的對話」。一輪擾攘過後，校長與在場約數十名學生再次進入會場，要求在沒有媒體的情況下進行閉門對話會。段校長與學生在兩小時後步出會場，與前次不同的是，眾人竟紛紛向校長道謝，而段校長也隨即向媒體宣布自己數個重要承諾。//<br />\n<br />\n原文：《校長閉門會議，融化了的異溫層&mdash;&mdash;一名香港中大學生的觀察和思考》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20191013-notes-cuhk-vice-chancellor-students-forum/?fbclid=IwAR35vYGyBxTi2muSh5r9HVNlcAeOeXKAyADj6HwfWJxCZwgDjQeVE8pN8ZE&amp;utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20191013-notes-cuhk-vice-chancellor-students-forum%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR35vYGyBxTi2muSh5r9HVNlcAeOeXKAyADj6HwfWJxCZwgDjQeVE8pN8ZE%26utm_medium%3Dcopy&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2F%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=40062a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20191013-notes-cuhk-vice-chancellor-students-forum/?fbclid=IwAR35vYGyBxTi2muSh5r9HVNlcAeOeXKAyADj6HwfWJxCZwgDjQeVE8pN8ZE&amp;utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media"},{"pid":"986f44e85363aed33806fa83d6d7ac3fd93c7dc0","tid":1661476,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a9931a6ebcc5667d3f054a05673bfa7818446a","tid":1661476,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫我推多次上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" d